</span></div>
        </li>
              <li>
          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/essay/home-face-grief-sylvia-petter" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/Petter-a.jpg?itok=lmNIJ8db" width="250" height="175" alt="An aged photograph of a couple walking along a beach" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

</a>

