          <div><div>  <a href="/blog/essay/when-dogs-could-talk-among-words-state-grace-n-scott-momaday" hreflang="en"><img loading="lazy" src="/sites/worldliteraturetoday.org/files/styles/medium_thumbnail/public/Momaday-Dogs-w.jpg?itok=VRmqiFjZ" width="250" height="175" alt="A painting of a dog standing on a cloud" typeof="foaf:Image" class="img-fluid image-style-medium-thumbnail" />

